title: By the King, a proclamation William R.
author: England and Wales. Sovereign (1694-1702 : William III)
publisher: Printed by Charles Bill, and the executrix of Thomas Newcomb ...,
notes: Reproduction of original in Huntington Library.
At end of text: Given at our court at Kensington the eighth day of February, 1699.
Proclamation ordering all Catholic priests and Jesuits out of England.
